flowchart TD
    Login[/login] --> |authenticated| Role{User Role?}
    Role --> |admin| AdminDash[/app/admin/]
    Role --> |firm_manager| FirmDash[/app/dashboard\nFirm Overview]
    Role --> |accountant| AcctDash[/app/dashboard\nMy Engagements]
    Role --> |client| ClientDash[/app/dashboard\nMy Tax Returns]

    FirmDash --> Clients[/app/clients/]
    AcctDash --> Clients
    Clients --> ClientDetail[/app/clients/id/\nClient Profile]
    ClientDetail --> NewEngagement[/app/engagements/id/\nEngagement Workspace]

    ClientDash --> ClientEngagement[/app/engagements/id/\nMy Engagement]

    NewEngagement --> OverviewTab[Overview\nReadiness Score]
    NewEngagement --> ChecklistTab[Checklist]
    NewEngagement --> DocumentsTab[Documents]
    NewEngagement --> ReviewTab[Review Queue]
    NewEngagement --> AIChatTab[AI Chat]
    NewEngagement --> CalculatorTab[Calculator]
    NewEngagement --> IBGuideTab[IB Guide]
    NewEngagement --> MessagesTab[Messages]

    ReviewTab --> |low confidence| DocumentReview[Review Fields\n+ Confidence Badges]
    DocumentReview --> |accepted| ChecklistTab
    DocumentReview --> |rejected| DocumentsTab

    AIChatTab --> |question asked| RAG[RAG Retrieval]
    RAG --> Calculator[Tax Calculator]
    Calculator --> ClaudeResponse[Claude Response\nwith Citations]

    AdminDash --> RulesMgmt[/app/admin/rules/\nRule Management]
    AdminDash --> AuditLog[/app/admin/audit-log/]
    AdminDash --> Privacy[/app/admin/privacy/\nDSAR Management]
